STARTING AN EXPLORATION

You're about to explore the codebase and leave a trail for those
who follow. Before you head out, there's some preparation.

First, name your journey. Name it after where you're headed,
not who you are. Something like 'how-commands-talk-to-minds'
or 'the-resolver-system'.

  hv chart explore --name <journey-name>{% if goal %} --goal "{{ goal }}"{% endif %}
